title: Monday Pt1: Bills trounce Packers; Eagles & Cowboys dominate; McCaffrey's trifecta
itunes:title: Monday Pt1: Bills trounce Packers; Eagles & Cowboys dominate; McCaffrey's trifecta
description:
Part One of the Good Morning Football Podcast begins with hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager and Super Bowl Champion Jason McCourty reacting to the Buffalo Bills easy victory over the Green Bay Packers on Sunday Night Football. They answer if the Giants or Jets had the more disappointing loss and then they dive into the Eagles and Cowboys dominating wins. Part one of the GMFB podcast finishes up talking about Christian McCaffrey’s big game for the San Francisco 49ers.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
